ack\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 31, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sni1710750486960.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sni1710750486960.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sni1710750486960.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qte1696845021070\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can add user-defined keyboard shortcut keys for various Uniface IDE actions or your\n\t\tapplications in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">[userkeys]</code> section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>\n\t\tfile. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qte1696845021070__section_cnz_cyb_bzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d700473e55\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">[userkeys]</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qte1696845021070__pre_fk5_b2c_bzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">action=key_combination</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">You can change the key_combination as per your requirement, but the action arguments\n\t\t\t\tare fixed. </p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example</strong>: <code class=\"ph codeph\">code.uppercase=Ctrl+U</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qte1696845021070__section_e1d_1fc_bzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d700473e82\">Settings</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following section displays the default supported <code class=\"ph codeph\">[userkeys]</code>\n\t\t\t\tsection settings.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sni1710750486960_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qte1696845021070__codeblock_wqw_dfc_bzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[userkeys]\nnav.ubar=Alt+D\nnav.message.frame=Ctrl+M\neditor.refresh=F5\neditor.close=Ctrl+F4\neditor.close.all=Ctrl+Shift+F4\neditor.next=Ctrl+Tab\neditor.previous=Ctrl+Shift+Tab\nbuild.compile=Ctrl+F7\nbuild.test=Ctrl+F5\nbuild.compile.test=Ctrl+Shift+F7\ncode.comment=Ctrl+K\ncode.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K\ncode.uppercase=Ctrl+U\ncode.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U\ncode.formatselection=Alt+F\ncode.formatdocument=Alt+Shift+F\ncode.search=Ctrl+F\ncode.searchandreplace=Ctrl+H\ncode.gotoline=Ctrl+G\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrf1692863383119.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Comment and uncomment code</a><p>You can comment and uncomment codes in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cxv1693905302584.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uppercase and lowercase code</a><p>You can uppercase and lowercase code in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwc1695725497353.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Adding user-defined keyboard shortcuts in the IDE</a><p>You can use the following default shortcut keys in the IDE to navigate inside the editor or trigger various supported actions with a keyboard, such as compile a current object or compile and test an object.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6400880\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6400880\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[userkeys] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 31, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 You can add user-defined keyboard shortcut keys for various Uniface IDE actions or your applications in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file. Description [userkeys] action=key_combination Copy You can change the key_combination as per your requirement, but the action arguments are fixed. Example : code.uppercase=Ctrl+U Settings The following section displays the default supported [userkeys] section settings. Explain this code [userkeys] nav.ubar=Alt+D nav.message.frame=Ctrl+M editor.refresh=F5 editor.close=Ctrl+F4 editor.close.all=Ctrl+Shift+F4 editor.next=Ctrl+Tab editor.previous=Ctrl+Shift+Tab build.compile=Ctrl+F7 build.test=Ctrl+F5 build.compile.test=Ctrl+Shift+F7 code.comment=Ctrl+K code.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K code.uppercase=Ctrl+U code.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U code.formatselection=Alt+F code.formatdocument=Alt+Shift+F code.search=Ctrl+F code.searchandreplace=Ctrl+H code.gotoline=Ctrl+G Copy Related Links Comment and uncomment code You can comment and uncomment codes in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu. Uppercase and lowercase code You can uppercase and lowercase code in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu. Adding user-defined keyboard shortcuts in the IDE You can use the following default shortcut keys in the IDE to navigate inside the editor or trigger various supported actions with a keyboard, such as compile a current object or compile and test an object. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}